quran[15]{c,v,t}:
  19,96,Be-shak jo eman laye hain aur jinhon ney shaeesta aemaal kiye hain unn kay liye Allah rehman mohabbat peda ker dey ga
  19,97,Hum ney iss quran ko teri zaban mein boht hi aasan ker diya hai kay tu iss kay zariye say perhezgaron ko khushkhabri dey aur jhagraloo logon ko dara dey
  19,98,Hum ney inn say pehlay boht si jamaten tabah ker di hain kiya inn mein say aik bhi aahat tu pata hai ya unn ki awaz ki bhanak bhi teray kaan mein parti hai
  20,1,Taahaa
  20,2,Hum ney yeh quran tujh per iss liye nahi utara kay tu mushaqqat mein parr jaye
  20,3,Bulkay uss ki naseehat kay liye jo Allah say darta hai
  20,4,Iss ka utarna uss ki taraf say hai jiss ney zamin ko aur buland aasmano ko peda kiya hai
  20,5,Jo rehman hai arsh per qaeem hai
  20,6,Jiss ki milkiyar aasmano aur zamin aur inn dono kay darmiyan aur (kurra-e-khak) kay neechay ki her aik cheez per hai
  20,7,Agar tu unchi baat kahey to woh to her aik posheeda bulkay posheeda say posheeda tar cheez ko bhi ba-khoobi janta hai
  20,8,Wohi Allah hai jiss kay siwa koi mabood nahi behtareen naam ussi kay hain
  20,9,Tujhay musa (alh-e-salam) ka qissa bhi maloom hai
  20,10,Jabkay uss ney aag dekh ker apney ghar walon say kaha kay tum zara si dare thehar jao mujhay aag dikhaee di hai. Boht mumkin hai kay mein iss ka koi angara tumharay pass laon yaa aag kay pass say rastay ki itlaa paon
  20,11,Jab woh wahan phonchay to awaz di gaee aey musa
  20,12,Yaqeenan mein hi tera perwerdigar hun to tu apni jootiyan utar dey kiyon kay tu pak maidan-e-toowa mein hai